{
  "episode_id": "2026-07-12",
  "chunks": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "听众朋友大家好，欢迎收听AI 每日先锋，今天是2026年7月12日。我是苏晴。",
      "start": 1.0,
      "duration": 7.314,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_001_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_001_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "大家好，我是周航。",
      "start": 8.763,
      "duration": 1.437,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_002_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_002_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "周航，你最近有没有被谷歌I/O刷屏？我打开社交媒体，满屏都是Gemini新版本和各种新功能，感觉整个科技圈都在讨论同一件事。",
      "start": 10.697,
      "duration": 13.148,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_003_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_003_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你还别说，我那天晚上专门熬夜看了发布会，结束之后脑子是懵的——倒不是某一项东西特别亮眼，而是它一口气扔出来的更新实在太多了。",
      "start": 24.298,
      "duration": 11.276,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_004_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_004_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "具体有多少？",
      "start": 35.979,
      "duration": 1.132,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_005_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_005_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "Google自己发了一篇博客，标题直接就叫\"100 things we announced at I/O 2026\"。你没听错，100项。",
      "start": 37.544,
      "duration": 9.099,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_006_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_006_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "这也太夸张了。以前苹果发布会也就十几个功能点，谷歌这是要把一整年的更新浓缩进一场活动里？",
      "start": 47.108,
      "duration": 10.057,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_007_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_007_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "问题是这100项不是凑数。我大致过了一遍，从Gemini模型的迭代、Android系统的AI化改造、Workspace里各种智能功能、开发者工具的更新，再到硬件生态，每个层面都有动作。",
      "start": 57.627,
      "duration": 14.561,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_008_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_008_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "那这意味着什么？是不是说Google已经把AI当成一个操作系统级别的战略来做了？",
      "start": 72.639,
      "duration": 5.965,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_009_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_009_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "说白了，这就是\"全栈AI化\"。以前大家比的是谁的模型跑分高、谁的对话能力强，现在Google直接把竞争维度拉高了一档——谁能先把AI揉进所有产品线里、构建完整的生态闭环，谁就是下一个十年的赢家。",
      "start": 79.104,
      "duration": 18.305,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_010_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_010_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "我觉得这个判断挺有意思的。你注意啊，它不是在做某个单一爆款，而是在铺一张网。",
      "start": 97.847,
      "duration": 7.532,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_011_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_011_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "对，这就是Google一贯的思路。它不需要在每个细分领域都拿第一，但它能保证你一天里只要碰电子产品，就绕不开它的AI能力。这种\"无处不在\"的渗透力，其实比单一爆款更难对付。",
      "start": 105.84,
      "duration": 15.519,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_012_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_012_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "那除了I/O这场大戏，有没有什么具体的技术让你眼前一亮？",
      "start": 121.804,
      "duration": 5.878,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_013_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_013_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "我个人最感兴趣的是Gemini 3.5 Live Translate，实时语音翻译。",
      "start": 128.156,
      "duration": 5.573,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_014_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_014_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "翻译工具现在不是满大街都是吗？谷歌翻译、DeepL一大堆，这有什么新鲜的？",
      "start": 134.156,
      "duration": 7.358,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_015_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_015_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你注意啊，传统翻译有个老毛病——要么延迟高，你说完了等两三秒才翻出来；要么就是机械感很重，听着像在跟Siri对话。Live Translate做的事情，就是同时把这两个问题给解决了。",
      "start": 141.978,
      "duration": 13.864,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_016_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_016_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "怎么解决的？",
      "start": 156.259,
      "duration": 0.914,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_017_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_017_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "它能做到几乎零延迟，而且翻译出来的语音听起来就像真人在跟你说话，语速、语调、甚至停顿都很自然。Google自己用的词是\"fluid, natural\"，翻译过来就是\"流畅且自然\"。",
      "start": 157.609,
      "duration": 14.256,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_018_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_018_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "我跟你说，这要是真能做到那种程度，对跨语言沟通的影响可就大了。你想想，以前出国旅行、跨国开会、跨语言谈恋爱都得靠翻译软件，磕磕绊绊的。如果以后真能像跟母语者聊天一样，那语言壁垒基本上就……",
      "start": 172.282,
      "duration": 17.783,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_019_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_019_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "就隐形了。这正是这项技术最值得琢磨的地方。它表面上是个翻译工具，底下撬动的却是教育、商务、文化交流的全球格局。一个中国学生可以无障碍听MIT的实时课程，一个非洲创业者能跟硅谷投资人像老乡一样聊天，地理和语言就不再是信息流通的瓶颈。",
      "start": 190.561,
      "duration": 23.442,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_020_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_020_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "嗯，这个想象空间确实大。不过我有个担心——这种技术会不会让某些行业受到冲击？比如同声传译员。",
      "start": 214.415,
      "duration": 8.795,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_021_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_021_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "这是个好问题。说白了，工具越强，对\"机械型\"岗位的替代就越快。但真正顶级的同传从来不只是翻译语言，他们翻译的是文化、语境、还有言外之意。这种需要深厚人类判断力的活儿，短期内AI还是啃不动的。",
      "start": 223.689,
      "duration": 17.26,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_022_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_022_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "行，那咱们从I/O这个大坑里出来，说几个轻快一点的。对了，Google还发了一份5月AI回顾，把过去一个月发布的重要更新串了一遍，感兴趣的朋友可以顺着去看看。",
      "start": 241.381,
      "duration": 15.369,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_023_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_023_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "还有一个我注意到的是，他们专门做了一篇\"12 major I/O moments\"，相当于从100项更新里挑出最值得关注的12个高光时刻，做了一个精华版。",
      "start": 257.218,
      "duration": 11.842,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_024_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_024_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "这挺贴心，毕竟不是每个人都有耐心看完100项。",
      "start": 269.55,
      "duration": 4.963,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_025_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_025_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "对，时间紧张的朋友可以先看那个12个版本，再根据兴趣点深挖。最后还有一条跟AI不太直接相关的——Google宣布在弗吉尼亚州投了一笔钱搞社区建设，重点是支持本地就业，还有扩大能源可负担性计划。",
      "start": 274.99,
      "duration": 19.089,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_026_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_026_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "AI公司现在也都在做基建类投资了。能源这块其实跟AI关系挺大的，毕竟数据中心是耗电大户。",
      "start": 294.497,
      "duration": 9.97,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_027_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_027_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你看出来了。算力需求在暴涨，电力供应就是命脉。Google这种提前布局能源基础设施的动作，本质上是在为下一个十年的AI竞赛做后勤保障——你光有模型不行，还得有电喂它。",
      "start": 304.906,
      "duration": 14.953,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_028_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_028_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "听你这么一说，AI这盘棋真的比我们想象的要大得多。",
      "start": 320.271,
      "duration": 3.962,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_029_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_029_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "是的，从模型到终端，从社区到能源，每个环节都在被重新连接。今天的节目就到这里，咱们明天接着聊。",
      "start": 324.726,
      "duration": 8.49,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_030_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_030_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "好了听众朋友们，以上就是今天的AI每日先锋。感谢收听，我们明天见！",
      "start": 333.625,
      "duration": 7.271,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_031_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_031_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "拜拜！",
      "start": 341.383,
      "duration": 0.697,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_032_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_032_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    }
  ]
}